==Korean==
===Adverb===
'''잘''' ''jal''
#Well
#:그림을 아주 '''잘''' 그린다 (''Geurim-eul jal geurinda'') [He] draws pictures well. 
#:''''잘''' 생각해 봐! (''Jal saenggak-hae bwa!'') Think '''carefully'''!
#Often
#At a good time, with fortunate timing
#:물어 볼 말이 있었는데 마침 잘 오셨어요. (''Mureo bol mal-i isseosseoneunde machim '''jal''' osyeosseoyo''). You have come at a good time, I have something to ask you.

